article.description: — Ricky Clemons had 15 points and 11 rebounds to lead Campbell to a 66-55 win over Maryland-Eastern Shore on Wednesday.
article.headline: Clemons lifts Campbell over Maryland-Eastern Shore 66-55
article.linkText: Clemons lifts Campbell over Maryland-Eastern Shore 66-55
article.story: BUIES CREEK, N.C. -- — Ricky Clemons had 15 points and 11 rebounds to lead Campbell to a 66-55 win over Maryland-Eastern Shore on Wednesday. Cedric Henderson Jr. had 13 points for Campbell (4-1). Messiah Thompson added 11 points. Austin McCullough had six rebounds. Zion Styles had 10 points for the Hawks (2-3). Nathaniel Pollard Jr. added eight rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
